[
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "My restaurant's quite small.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我的餐厅很小一间\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "And I still cook outside.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我到现在都还是在路边做菜 ‎（无法提供确切等候时间\n‎非常抱歉）\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "No one comes to Jay Fai's place for the ambiance.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎大家来光顾痣姐热炒\n‎不是因为餐厅气氛佳\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "They come because the food is delicious.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎客人都是为了美食来的 ‎客人会上门是因为这里的食物很美味\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Even as a kid\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎在我还小的时候 ‎我每天一睁开眼想到的就是工作\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I woke up thinking about work.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我每天一睁开眼想到的就是工作\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I'd do it every day if I could.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎要是可以的话 我每天都想工作\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Every day, I wake up at 10:30 in the morning.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我每天早上10点半起床\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "My staff arrives around noon to help.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我的员工大概中午左右会来帮忙\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I'm old, but I always tell them,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我虽然老了 但我还是常跟他们说\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "\"You may be younger, but I am stronger.\"\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎“你们比我年轻\n‎但我比你们都要强壮”\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "By 2:30 in the afternoon, I'm ready.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎下午2点半之前\n‎我就会开始为自己做准备\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "When I walk into my station,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我只要一走进料理台\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I have to be focused.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎就一定要全神贯注\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I am meticulous about every dish that I serve.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我对每一道端上桌的菜都一丝不苟\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Everything must be flawless.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎每个细节都必须要完美无缺\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "No matter what's going on. No matter how tired I am.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎不管我有多累 不管发生什么事\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I cook every dish myself.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我都一定亲自下厨\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I want it to be the best.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我希望我的料理是最棒的\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Because I'm not just a street cook.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎因为我不只是个路边摊小贩\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I'm a chef.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我是个大厨\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "My older brother opened our noodle stall\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我哥哥是第一个在素坤逸38巷\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "on Sukhumvit 38 road.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎开面摊的人\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Back then, over 30 years ago,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎三十几年前的时候\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "the place was surrounded by bars.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎这附近到处都是酒吧\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "After the party-goers finished, they would come to eat.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎在夜店狂欢到深夜的人\n‎都会来这里吃东西\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "We would sell until 4 or 5 in the morning.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我们会营业到凌晨4、5点\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Last year, the landlord suddenly shut us down.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎去年地主突然不准我们在那做生意了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Most of our fellow vendors quit and moved back to their hometowns.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎很多摊贩都不想做了 搬回老家去了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "But our customers kept calling.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎可是我们的客人一直打电话来\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "\"Hello? Hello? Where are you?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎“喂？你们搬到哪去了？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Will you start selling again?\"\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎还会继续做生意吗？”\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "My brother suggested re-opening near my house.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我哥哥建议我重新开张 ‎把面摊开在我家附近 比较方便\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Our customers missed us so much they took taxis out to see us.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我们的客人太想我们了\n‎就搭出租车来吃面\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "The noodles cost 60 baht, the taxi costs over 300 baht.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎一碗面才60泰铢\n‎光搭出租车就要超过300泰铢\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "They were so happy to come out here and eat.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎大家来这里吃面都很开心\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "We were so happy to see them.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我们看到大家也都很开心\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I grew up in a slum.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我从小在贫民窟长大\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "In a bad neighborhood behind a market.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎就住在菜市场后面乱七八糟的地方\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Mom sold rice porridge and noodles at the market.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我妈在市场卖粥跟鸡肉汤面\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "She had to sell it a lot.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎要卖很多碗才能维持生计\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Dad was an opium addict.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我爸是个鸦片成瘾者\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Sometimes he ran away. We didn't know where he was.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎有时候他会离家出走\n‎没人知道他去哪里\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "So I became a seamstress.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎所以我就去当裁缝\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I sewed dresses all day and cut fabric all night.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎整天都在剪布料、卷布料\n‎然后熬夜缝衣服\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I made sure there was rice to eat.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我要负责一家人的温饱\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I spent ten years as a seamstress.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎做了整整十年裁缝的工作\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Time flew by when I did this sort of work.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎当裁缝的日子 一眨眼就过了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I was content.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我很满意这种生活\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "But then one day, I was sewing...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎但有一天 当我在忙针线活的时候…\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Boom! A stairway collapsed.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎“砰”的一声 我旁边的楼梯塌了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Fire erupted.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎失火了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Everyone shouted, \"Run!\"\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎大家都喊着：“快跑啊！”\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I ran outside, looked back and everything was gone.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我冲到外面回头看\n‎一切都化为灰烬了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I had nothing left.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我什么都没了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "After everything burned down, all I had were the pajamas on my back.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎等火灭了之后 我只剩下身上的睡衣\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "My sewing machine was gone, all my tools were gone.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我的缝纫机烧毁了 ‎其他工具也没了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I was twenty-five years old.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我那年才二十几岁\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I didn't know what to do.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎不知道该怎么办\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "One day, I was watching my mom sell noodles across from the market.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎在那之后\n‎我开始会去看我妈在市场卖面\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I noticed how slowly she cooked.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我就去帮她的忙 ‎有一天\n‎我发现她跟我妹妹煮面的速度很慢\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Four to five customers were just standing there, waiting for their food.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎四、五个客人站在那边等她们煮面\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I was frustrated.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我很着急\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I told her I wanted to cook.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我就跟她说换我来煮\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "She told me I couldn't do it.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎她说我做不来\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "\"Okay, you don't think I can do this?\"\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我心想：“你认为我办不到是吗？”\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "That night I grabbed the wok,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎那天晚上 我拿了炒锅\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I started stir-frying noodles.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎就开始炒面\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I practiced by myself every night. Ate that food every night.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我每天晚上都自己练习\n‎再自己把它吃光\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "At one point I poured oil into a wok and forgot about it.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎有一次 我忘了自己在锅倒了油\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "When I saw the oil burning, I dumped it all out.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎等我发现时 油都滚了\n‎我只好把油倒掉\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I got so mad, I threw noodles into the pan,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我实在太气了 就把面丢到锅子里\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "and stirred them furiously.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎气急败坏地乱炒一通\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "The heat alone browned them nicely.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎没想到 大火把面炒成漂亮的焦黄色\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I didn't need any oil.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎一滴油都用不着\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "They had a wonderful taste and aroma.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎吃起来又香又美味\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "The next day,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎隔天\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I asked Mom for her wok.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我跟我妈要了她的炒锅\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "She let me have it. It was all up to me.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎她让步了 让我掌厨\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "When I started to cook, the customers saw I had talent.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎客人看到我做菜 都夸我有天分\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Right then, I began to see my path.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎从那时候开始我就走上了厨师这条路\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "-Are these my rice noodles? -Yes.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎-这是我的细河粉吗？\n‎-对\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Weigh them again.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎再秤一次 孩子\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I need one kilo,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我只要一公斤\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "this is nearly two.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎这里快要两公斤了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "These mushrooms are too small.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎这些蘑菇有点小\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I need two pieces, not three.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎对切就好 不要切成三片\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I love every dish that I cook.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我爱我煮的每一道菜\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "You have to love them to cook them properly, down to every little detail.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎你要喜欢自己煮的菜\n‎煮的时候每个小细节都要精益求精\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Especially, tom yum.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎特别是冬阴汤这道菜\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "The stock soup must be rich and tasty, that's very important.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎重点在于高汤一定要又浓又香\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "You start with lots of bones to make the broth.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎先用大量的骨头去熬\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "And you just keep adding bones,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎熬煮的过程再持续加入骨头\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "bird's eye chilies, fish sauce, and lime juice.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎鸟眼辣椒、鱼露、青柠汁\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Do you know how delicious it is?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎你都不知道有多好吃\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "What about stir-fried noodles or tom yum?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎-有什么事吗？\n‎-小姐 请问你能推荐其他的菜吗？ ‎要不要来点醉猫炒河粉 ‎-或者是冬阴汤？\n‎-好啊 那就来一碗冬阴汤\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Street cooks don't make much money.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎卖街头小吃很单纯\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "They're just out there cooking late into the night.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎就是要在外头煮到深夜\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Just like me when I didn't have a permanent shophouse.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎像过去的我一样 没有固定的店面\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "By the time I was 30, I was responsible for my whole family.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎等到我30多岁时 ‎就要负责养家了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I was right on the street.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我在路边摆摊\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Chicken noodles, that's all I sold.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎菜单上就只有一道鸡肉汤面\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Sometimes I cooked until 4:00 or 5:00 a.m.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎要不停地煮 ‎有时要煮到清晨4、5点\n‎才能上床睡觉\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Life was very hard.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎生活过得很苦\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I had to put all my tables out on the sidewalk.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎餐桌椅都得摆在人行道上\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Sometimes, the authorities would chase us off.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎有时候 警察还会来赶我们走\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "On nights when it rained\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎要是碰到晚上下雨\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "or when they didn't let us put out tables,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎或是警察不让我们摆摊的日子\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "we were doomed.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎那就完了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I was trying hard to make money, but I was struggling.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我很努力工作赚钱\n‎但这种情况让我走投无路\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I had to do something.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我知道我得想办法解决\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "So, I took a risk.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎所以我冒险赌了一把\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I borrowed some money.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我借了点钱\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "And I bought some prawns.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎买了些虾\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Tiger prawns, very fresh.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎非常新鲜的草虾\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I set the price at 120 baht.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎把价格订在120泰铢\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "One guy balked, said it was only a shrimp pad thai.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎当时有人说：“不过是道炒河粉嘛”\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I told him these prawns were totally different.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我回说：“这些可不是一般的虾\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Don't compare them to anyone else's.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎不许你拿其他的虾来相提并论”\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "He ate them once and never ordered chicken again.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎他尝了一次\n‎之后就再没点过鸡肉料理\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I knew the dish was a success.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我就知道这道菜成功了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I started to look to expensive things, like seafood.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我开始研究像海鲜这类的高价食材\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Higher quality ingredients meant higher prices.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎品质越好的食材\n‎就代表能卖越好的价钱\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "That's how I got the money to rent my shophouse.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我就是这样赚到租店面的钱的\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "No matter where we go,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我们不管要去哪\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "the journey begins with curry.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎都要先吃一碗咖喱再上路\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Jek Pui was my father.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎杰贝是我父亲的名字\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "He studied how to make curry before he left China.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎他是从中国来曼谷的时候\n‎学会煮咖喱的\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "When my father could cook curry,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我父亲学会做咖喱之后\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "his family sent him to Thailand to make a new life.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎他的亲戚叫他带着全家大小\n‎来泰国讨生活\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "We've been here for over 70 years.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我们已经来这里70多年了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "He worked hard developing his recipe.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎他很努力研发自己的食谱\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Sometimes he got it right, sometimes wrong, but he kept at it.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎有时成功 有时失败 但他没有放弃\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "At 13, I started helping him out.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我13岁就开始帮他的忙\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "My father only sold pork and beef curries.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我父亲只卖猪肉跟牛肉咖喱\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I created our other dishes myself.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎其他口味都是我开发出来的\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "We've added green curry with meatballs or chicken and pork Penang.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎现在菜单上还有肉丸或鸡肉绿咖喱\n‎跟猪肉帕能咖喱\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "When customers loved them, that meant the recipes were right.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎要是客人喜欢吃\n‎就代表这份食谱成功了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Back when I moved into my restaurant,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎等我终于搬进我的餐馆之后\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I still called myself a street cook.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我还是称自己是路边摊\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I opened my shop in the evenings.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我在晚上开店\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "My customers came from bars and gambling joints.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎从酒吧或赌场出来的客人会来我这里\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "The ones who really loved to eat\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎当中有一些对吃很讲究的人\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "would gather around to watch me cook.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎会聚集在旁边看我煮菜\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I saw an opportunity.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我发现了商机\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Anyone could stir-fry pad thai.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎每一个人都会炒河粉\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I wanted to do something great.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎所以我想做点特别的\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I loved crab omelettes.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我想要做蛋包蟹\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "But I wanted to make something different.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎但就算是蛋包蟹\n‎我也要做得跟别人与众不同\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "So I taught myself to make Japanese omelettes.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎所以我自学做日式蛋卷\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I added a lot of crabs, nearly a pound.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我加了大量的蟹肉 差不多有半公斤\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I flattened and rolled them.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎先铺平再卷\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "When I took my first bite, oh ho!\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我吃了第一口…\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "It was so beautiful, I'd done it.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎实在太好吃 我做到了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I had something special to sell.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我终于有独家菜色了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "People started to talk about my food.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎大家开始讨论我的料理\n‎客人都慕名而来\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "The gambling houses started calling in lots of orders.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎赌场开始打电话来大量点餐\n‎一次就点好几十份\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "We started selling so many crab omelettes,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我们卖了好多好多煎蛋卷\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "sometimes we ran out of eggs.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎有时候蛋都不够用\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Is Khun Da here?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎-妲小姐在现场吗？\n‎-在的\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Please come in.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎这边请\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "From that point on, I started to build a whole new menu.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎从那时候开始 我就开始构思新菜单\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "New dishes just came to me.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎新菜色源源不绝\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Famous high ranked people and politicians started to turn up.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎大人物跟政治家也纷纷出现\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "They would ask for special things.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎他们都想吃私房菜色\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I had so many dishes to recommend.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我们的菜单越来越长 ‎超过100种菜色\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I was proud of my bravery and I never regretted it.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我对自己大胆的决定非常自豪\n‎也从不觉得后悔\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "For 40 years, I worked almost every day.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎四十年来 我几乎从不休息\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "And then one day, I got a call.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎突然有一天 我接到一通电话\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Somebody was hosting a gala dinner.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎有人邀请我去参加一场大型晚宴\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I don't like to close my restaurant for anything.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我不喜欢随便休息\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "But I took the day off for the party.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎但我请了一天假去参加那场派对\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "All of a sudden, my daughter said,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎突然间 我女儿说\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "\"Mom, they called your name.\"\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎“妈 他们在叫你的名字”\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I won the award.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我得了大奖\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "The Michelin star.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎米其林一星\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Right then, it seemed like I couldn't breathe.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎那时候我高兴到快不能呼吸了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I was happy. The happiest.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎那是我有史以来最高兴的时刻\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "The next day,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎隔天\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "there was a big crowd in front of my restaurant.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我的餐厅门口就挤满了人\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Everyone wanted to take my picture.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎大家都想找我拍照\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "People had to start reserving tables.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎人多到开始要订位\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "My daughter quit her job to help me manage it all.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我女儿辞了工作来帮我\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "When chefs started coming to my shop to eat, they called me \"Chef.\"\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎有其他大厨来我店里吃饭\n‎他们也叫我“大厨”\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Wow... I am a chef.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎“真的吗？我是个大厨？”\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I can't describe how proud I was.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我无法形容自己有多自豪\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Put the bigger chunks in here, don't torture the customers.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎把大块的蟹肉放进来\n‎不要亏待我们的客人\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I've been cooking for a long time.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我已经当厨师很长一段时间了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Whenever anyone asks, I say I'm not tired.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎每次有人问我 我都说我不会累\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I know my strength.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎我知道自己的能耐\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I have faith in charcoal fires and iron woks.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎炭火跟铁锅就是我的信念\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "They taught me to be clever.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎它们教我变聪明\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "They taught me to be brave.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎教我变勇敢\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "So if I still have the strength, I will continue cooking.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎所以只要我还有体力的一天\n‎就会继续做菜\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "This is me.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        ‎这就是我\n                        \n                    "
    }
  }
]